To be compiled with gnu make and 
mingw-w64 in ubuntu.


pkts to install:

binutils-mingw-w64-i686                         
binutils-mingw-w64-x86-64                       
g++-mingw-w64-i686                              
g++-mingw-w64-i686-posix                        
g++-mingw-w64-i686-win32                        
g++-mingw-w64-x86-64                            
g++-mingw-w64-x86-64-posix                      
g++-mingw-w64-x86-64-win32                      
gcc-mingw-w64-base:amd64                        
gcc-mingw-w64-i686                              
gcc-mingw-w64-i686-posix                        
gcc-mingw-w64-i686-posix-runtime                
gcc-mingw-w64-i686-win32                        
gcc-mingw-w64-i686-win32-runtime                
gcc-mingw-w64-x86-64                            
gcc-mingw-w64-x86-64-posix                      
gcc-mingw-w64-x86-64-posix-runtime              
gcc-mingw-w64-x86-64-win32                      
gcc-mingw-w64-x86-64-win32-runtime              
libz-mingw-w64                                  
mingw-w64-common                                
mingw-w64-i686-dev                              
mingw-w64-x86-64-dev                            


options to make:
AMD64=1 -- build 64bit executable
LTO=1 -- perform link time optimizations

example:
make AMD64=1 LTO=1 -j8 # build 64bit exe with link time optimizations in 8 threads

